snippet.title: Black & White PC game Trailer
snippet.description:
This video clip shows you a simple relay of what this game is about. The building of your villages and towns, and some of the options you have about what to build. You will see the simple hand tool as it's used and in the end a view of a medium sized town.

Hey Everyone don't forget to Subscribe and add me as a friend or family pleeeaaseee and have a nice pleasante day everyone!!
